Textmate Bundle for Webrat

Just a simple collection of snippets.  The snippets are intended to be used by people using the RSPec Story bundle and/or the Cucumber bundle.

How to install:
mkdir -p ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles/
cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
git clone git://github.com/bmabey/webrat-tmbundle.git Webrat.tmbundle
In TextMate:
From your drop down menu, select Bundles -> Bundle Editor -> Reload Bundles

